## New strings
- `IOS_PROFILE_MESSAGE: "Message"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_AUDIO: "Call"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_VIDEO: "Video"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_ADD_FRIEND: "Add Friend"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_PENDING: "Pending"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_MUTUAL_FRIENDS: "{count, plural, =0 {0 Mutual Friends} one {1 Mutual Friend} other {{count} Mutual Friends}}"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_MUTUAL_GUILDS: "{count, plural, =0 {0 Mutual Servers} one {1 Mutual Server} other {{count} Mutual Servers}}"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_MUTUAL_FRIENDS_PLACEHOLDER: "Mutual Friends"`
- `IOS_PROFILE_MUTUAL_GUILDS_PLACEHOLDER: "Mutual Servers`

## New strings
- `LFG_SAVE_BUTTON: "Save"`
- `LFG_SIDEBAR_DESCRIPTION: "Group description"`
- `LFG_SIDEBAR_SIZE: "Size"`
- `LFG_SIDEBAR_SIZE_NUMBER: "!!{groupSize}!! People"`
- `LFG_SIDEBAR_STATUS: "Status"`
- `LFG_SIDEBAR_STATUS_ACTIVE: "Open"`
- `LFG_SIDEBAR_STATUS_EXPIRED: "Expired"`
- `LFG_LISTING_EXPIRATION_EXPLAIN: "Groups automatically expire after 12 hours of inactivity"`

- New action type (iOS): `CALL_KIT_UPDATE_SETTINGS`

## New strings
- `FORM_LABEL_MOBILE_NOTIFICATIONS_CALL_DESC: "Integrate calls with Phone app."`
- `INCOMING_CALL_DM: "!!{username}!! is calling"`
- `INCOMING_CALL_GDM: "Incoming group call from !!{name}!!"`

- New action types (iOS): `GUILD_PREMIUM_SUBSCRIBE_MODAL_OPEN_IOS`, `GUILD_PREMIUM_SUBSCRIBE_MODAL_CLOSE_IOS`
- New user settings section (iOS): `PREMIUM_GUILD_SUBSCRIPTION: "Nitro Server Boost"`
- New constant: `PREMIUM_YEARLY_DISCOUNT_PERCENT = 16`

## New strings (iOS)
- `PREMIUM_CHAT_PERKS_PREMIUM_GUILD_SUBSCRIPTION: "Boost your favorite server!"`
- `PREMIUM_GUILD_SUBSCRIPTION_SUBTITLE_MOBILE_1: "Use your Nitro powers to boost a Server you've joined! Boosting a Server allows it to progress towards levels. Each Level gives collective perks for the entire server."`
- `PREMIUM_GUILD_SUBSCRIPTION_SUBTITLE_MOBILE_2: "Boosting a server activates a 7-day cooldown. You may not boost another server until this cooldown is finished even if you remove your boost. [Learn more about Nitro Server Boosting.]({helpdeskArticle})"`
- `PREMIUM_CHAT_PERKS_SIMPLE_TITLE_IOS: "Just want super powered chat perks? Get Nitro Classic"`
- `PREMIUM_GUILD_PERKS_MODAL_BLURB_MOBILE_1: "For each level achieved, members of this server will help unlock perks for everyone. These perks are only in effect within the server."`
- `PREMIUM_GUILD_PERKS_MODAL_BLURB_MOBILE_2: "**Boosters get: Member List icon, new evolving badge, and a Booster-only role.** [Learn more about Nitro Server Boosting.]({helpdeskArticle})"`

- Go Live is officially rolling out (even further)!
- New Go Live server boost and Nitro perks
  - Server Boost tier 1 unlocks up to 720p 60fps and tier 2 unlocks up to 1080p 60fps
##
- Endpoint removed: `RTC_QUALITY_REPORT: "/rtc/quality-report"`
- Analytic event removed: `video_stream_quality_changed`
- Experiments removed: `MOBILE_GUILD_VERIFICATION_NOTIF: "2019-05_mobile_large_server_verification_notif"`, `STORE_DIRECTORY_LAYOUT: "2019-01_store_directory_layout"`
- New icon: `LfgListingsChannelLimited`
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/18150845/63120536-bb549300-bfa2-11e9-960d-bca5a423450c.png)
- New perk icon: `STREAM: 7`

## Strings
#### Updated
- `STREAM`: `"Stream"` -> `"Go Live"`
- `LIVE_BETA_DESCRIPTION`: `"Welcome to the stream! We're working on making it beta"` -> `"Welcome to the stream! Go Live is in beta. Sorry ‘bout any hiccups"`
- `STREAM_PREVIEW_PAUSED`: `"Streamer Preview Paused"` -> `"Your stream is still running!"`
- `ACTIVITY_PANEL_GO_LIVE_TOOLTIP_NO_PERMISSION_IN_VOICE`: `"You can't stream into this voice channel."` -> `"You can’t stream into this server."`
- `ACTIVITY_PANEL_GO_LIVE_HOTSPOT_HEADER`: `"Go Live to stream your game directly to your friends!"` -> `"Go Live to stream gameplay directly to your friends!"`
#### Added
- `STREAM_CHANNEL_DESCRIPTION: "Members with this permission can stream into this channel."`
- `GUILD_SETTINGS_GUILD_PREMIUM_PERK_TITLE_TIER_1_STREAMING: "720p 60fps Go Live streams"`
- `GUILD_SETTINGS_GUILD_PREMIUM_PERK_DESCRIPTION_TIER_1_STREAMING: "Share your high-quality gameplay with high-quality video streaming."`
- `GUILD_SETTINGS_GUILD_PREMIUM_PERK_TITLE_TIER_2_STREAMING: "1080p 60fps Go Live streams"`
- `GUILD_SETTINGS_GUILD_PREMIUM_PERK_DESCRIPTION_TIER_2_STREAMING: "Share your high-quality gameplay with high-quality video streaming."`
- `STREAM_PREVIEW_PAUSED_SUBTEXT: "We’ve just paused this preview to save your resources."`
- `STREAM_REPORT_RATING_BODY_STREAMER: "Tell us about your streaming experience."`
- `PREMIUM_CHAT_PERKS_TITLE_STREAMING: "Better Go Live Streams"`
- `PREMIUM_CHAT_PERKS_DESCRIPTION_STREAMING: "Stream at source with Nitro or up to a crisp 1080p 60fps with Nitro Classic."`
- `PREMIUM_CHAT_PERKS_STREAMING_MOBILE: "Better Go Live streams: Stream at source with Nitro or up to a crisp 1080 60fps with Nitro Classic"`
- `LFG_EMPTY_STATE_NOTE_2: "Create your own group to find people to play with!"`
- `LFG_UNKNOWN_MEMBER_TOOLTIP: "This user isn't a member of this server"`
- `LFG_SOMETHING_WENT_WRONG: "Oops, something went wrong! You may need to try again later"`
